{
  "stem": "812.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a very frightening time for my mother, in particular, because when my father was taken away we had no idea where he was and-- or whether we would ever see him again.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- but then when he was released, we continued with our preparations to emigrate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we left Hoya and went to Hanover.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in Hanover, we were there for just a few months and then left for Holland from where we were to sail to the United States.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Hoya is a very small town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, my-- my mother lives here in Queens, Far Rockaway, and the buildings surrounding where my mother lives now have more people in it than the little town of Hoya had.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were maybe 3,000 or 4,000 people is it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father was one of six children, and his siblings-- some of his siblings also lived with us in Hoya in the same house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was told that we had our own apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My grandparents lived in one apartment, we-- on one level of the house, and we lived in another level, and then the store was downstairs.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a very well-established store and a very well thought of business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] as far as holidays, we were as observant as we possibly could be in a small town such as Hoya.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a synagogue and-- and maybe, I believe, seven or eight Jewish families is-- is all.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And that's about all that I believe is--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a shoe business, men, women, and children shoes, as well as clothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it, I think, was one of the largest shoe and clothing stores in the little town of Hoya.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
